| Component         | Pin Name       | ESP32 GPIO Pin |
| ----------------- | -------------- | -------------- |
| Water Temp Sensor | DS18B20 Data   | GPIO 4 (D4)    |
| Turbidity Sensor  | Analog Output  | GPIO 34 (VP)   |
| Relay             | IN Pin         | GPIO 5 (D5)    |
| Servo Motor       | Control Signal | GPIO 13 (D13)  |
| OLED Display      | SDA            | GPIO 21        |
|                   | SCL            | GPIO 22        |
